message: This title has never actually been used for the game and has always been a fan term. Also GioGio > JoJo as per [[WP:MOS]]

"Vento Aureo" is a title only used in Italian localized volumes of the series and in non-canonical video games. The series has always been "黄金の風" (Ōgon no Kaze) in its source country, and official volumes were never actually Western localized.
